        "$:/plugins/tesseract/ExtendedInfo/Readme": {
            "created": "20180214233019927",
            "text": "This plugin adds the following info tiddlers on loading wiki.

* browserCodeName
* browserName
* browserVersion
* cookiesEnabled
* platform
* user-agentHeader
* browserLanguage
* browserOnline

You can find them at tiddlers that will be named like `$:/info/<property name>`. eg: [[$:/info/user-agentHeader]]",
            "title": "$:/plugins/tesseract/ExtendedInfo/Readme",
